From 5b4ca804792a3128ee56ac74a390358fabba6fa3 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Eric Huang <echuang@realtek.com>
Date: Fri, 6 Dec 2024 13:57:12 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] wifi: rtw89: ps: update data for firmware and settings for hardware before/after PS
Git-commit: 5b4ca804792a3128ee56ac74a390358fabba6fa3
Patch-mainline: v6.14-rc1
References: jsc#PED-14425

For MLO supported IC, send H2C command to firmware before PS with link
information for each PHY for MLO to work properly. And re-init hardware
settings regarding to RX descriptor information after PS.

Signed-off-by: Eric Huang <echuang@realtek.com>
Signed-off-by: Ping-Ke Shih <pkshih@realtek.com>
Link: https://patch.msgid.link/20241206055716.18598-4-pkshih@realtek.com
Acked-by: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>

---
